name: Murky's - Spread Ass Embed
description:
Do you want to support me? Consider being a patron on Patreon to vote on train polls and access stuff early. ❤️

My first pose embed so it has some issues but I'll update it in future.

Known Issues:

1- Instead of cropping i added 512 512 white background on images and this causing white borders appearing on images time to time.

2?- Sometime Embed does too much gaping but it's up to your taste if it's an issue or not 0.0 ... You can try giving less weight to the embed like 0.8 for less gaping

Trained with 120 image and 3000 steps with clip skip 2. Tested on Anythingv3 and Corneo's 7th Heaven Mix

I hope you guys like it. I also open character polls and requests in my Discord server feel free to drop and say hi ^^
